text: Hybolasius cristatellus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1876. It is known from New Zealand.BioLib.cz - Hybolasius cristatellus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1876
title: Hybolasius cristatellus
